<% meta title: "Home", description: "A stakeholder update platform for founders only." %>

<!-- hero -->
<div class="relative">
  <main class="lg:relative">
    <div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-7xl pt-16 pb-20 text-center lg:py-48 lg:text-left">
      <div class="px-4 sm:px-8 lg:w-1/2 xl:pr-16">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-5xl xl:text-6xl">
          <span class="block xl:inline">Dear Founders,</span>
          <span class="block text-brand-orange xl:inline">you're not alone.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="mx-auto mt-3 max-w-md text-lg text-gray-500 sm:text-xl md:mt-5 md:max-w-3xl">Founder Digest is a first of its kind platform for sharing private company updates with other founders.</p>
        <p class="mx-auto mt-3 max-w-md text-lg text-gray-500 sm:text-xl md:mt-5 md:max-w-3xl">Memberships are manually approved, and you can't read another founder's updates without sharing yours first.</p>
        <div class="mt-10 sm:flex sm:justify-center lg:justify-start">
          <div class="rounded-md shadow">
            <a href="#pricing" class="flex w-full items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-transparent bg-brand-blue hover:bg-brand-blue-dark px-8 py-3 text-base font-medium text-white md:py-4 md:px-10 md:text-lg">Get Started</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative h-64 w-full sm:h-72 md:h-96 lg:absolute lg:inset-y-0 lg:right-0 lg:h-full lg:w-1/2">
      <img class="absolute inset-0 h-full w-full object-cover" src="<%= asset_url 'founder-digest-hero.png' %>" alt="">
    </div>
  </main>
</div>

<!-- features -->
<div class="bg-white py-20 sm:py-24 lg:py-32">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-xl px-6 lg:max-w-7xl lg:px-8">
    <dl class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-16 lg:grid lg:grid-cols-3">
      <div>
        <dt>
          <div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-brand-orange text-white">
            <!-- Heroicon name: outline/globe-alt -->
            <svg class="h-8 w-8" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 21a9.004 9.004 0 008.716-6.747M12 21a9.004 9.004 0 01-8.716-6.747M12 21c2.485 0 4.5-4.03 4.5-9S14.485 3 12 3m0 18c-2.485 0-4.5-4.03-4.5-9S9.515 3 12 3m0 0a8.997 8.997 0 017.843 4.582M12 3a8.997 8.997 0 00-7.843 4.582m15.686 0A11.953 11.953 0 0112 10.5c-2.998 0-5.74-1.1-7.843-2.918m15.686 0A8.959 8.959 0 0121 12c0 .778-.099 1.533-.284 2.253m0 0A17.919 17.919 0 0112 16.5c-3.162 0-6.133-.815-8.716-2.247m0 0A9.015 9.015 0 013 12c0-1.605.42-3.113 1.157-4.418" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p class="mt-6 text-lg font-semibold leading-8 tracking-tight text-gray-900">Give and Get</p>
        </dt>
        <dd class="mt-2 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">Every month you have an opportunity to write about your company's recent performance. So long as you share something, you'll receive a hand-picked newsletter with updates from other founders.</dd>
      </div>

      <div>
        <dt>
          <div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-brand-orange text-white">
            <!-- Heroicon name: outline/scale -->
            <svg class="h-8 w-8" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 3v17.25m0 0c-1.472 0-2.882.265-4.185.75M12 20.25c1.472 0 2.882.265 4.185.75M18.75 4.97A48.416 48.416 0 0012 4.5c-2.291 0-4.545.16-6.75.47m13.5 0c1.01.143 2.01.317 3 .52m-3-.52l2.62 10.726c.122.499-.106 1.028-.589 1.202a5.988 5.988 0 01-2.031.352 5.988 5.988 0 01-2.031-.352c-.483-.174-.711-.703-.59-1.202L18.75 4.971zm-16.5.52c.99-.203 1.99-.377 3-.52m0 0l2.62 10.726c.122.499-.106 1.028-.589 1.202a5.989 5.989 0 01-2.031.352 5.989 5.989 0 01-2.031-.352c-.483-.174-.711-.703-.59-1.202L5.25 4.971z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p class="mt-6 text-lg font-semibold leading-8 tracking-tight text-gray-900">Private and Confidential</p>
        </dt>
        <dd class="mt-2 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">Following membership acceptance, users agree to mutual confidentiality. This is a trust-based platform for founders who want to learn from and help each other, not an entrepreneur gossip tabloid.</dd>
      </div>

      <div>
        <dt>
          <div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-brand-orange text-white">
            <!-- Heroicon name: outline/bolt -->
            <svg class="h-8 w-8" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.75 13.5l10.5-11.25L12 10.5h8.25L9.75 21.75 12 13.5H3.75z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p class="mt-6 text-lg font-semibold leading-8 tracking-tight text-gray-900">Networking 2.0</p>
        </dt>
        <dd class="mt-2 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600"><i>"Hi, what do you do?"</i> is dead. Connect directly with other founders in our network by simply replying to their updates. Your message will be sent directly to them.</dd>
      </div>
    </dl>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- pricing -->
